1.title: How to Do Dry Caving
1.plot: Discover Florida's mysterious inner world with Chad Crawford as he explores dry caves in Ocala. Plus Chef Justin Timineri shows you how to make Florida-style Sangria, bursting with fruit and flavor. Then, Chad's diving into the sparkling waters of Crystal River for some face-time with Florida's beloved manatees.
